[section#expr.bit.and
    [:en] Bitwise AND operator
    [:zh_CN] 按位与运算符

[:en]
[%expression[!bitwise AND]]
[%operator[!bitwise]]
[%operator[!bitwise AND]]
[%[`&][%operator[!bitwise AND]]]
[:zh_CN]
[%表达式[!按位与～]]
[%运算符[!按位～]]
[%运算符[!按位与～]]
[%[`&][%运算符[!按位与～]]]
]

[syntax]
[rule and-expression [:zh_CN] 与表达式 ]
    [| equality-expression ]
    [| and-expression [`&] equality-expression ]
[rule:end]
[syntax:end]

[para]
[:en]
The usual arithmetic conversions ([#expr.arith.conv]) are performed; the result
is the bitwise [$:sc AND] function of the operands.
[:zh_CN]
实施一般算术转换（[#expr.arith.conv]）；其结果为操作数的按位与函数。

[:en]
The operator applies only to integral or unscoped enumeration operands.
[:zh_CN]
该运算符仅适用于整型或无作用域枚举操作数。
